-- Finmeccanica to present new business plan in January - CEO
-- By Danilo Masoni
-- Thu Nov 06, 2014 03:56AM EST
-- None



MILAN, Nov 6 (Reuters) - Finmeccanica <SIFI.MI> will present to the market its new business plan at the end of January following board approval the same month, Chief Executive Mauro Moretti said on Thursday.

Speaking on a conference call on its nine-month results, Moretti said Finmeccanica had given bidders for its rail assets a Nov. 17 deadline to present their offers.